Run the following in claude ai

Create SKILL.md file for python chatbot
Should be a multi turn API conversations. 
Keep full conversation history and send to Claude as part of API requests (most recent 20)
API keys should be in .env. 
Use APIError and RateLimitError for stable chatbot responses
Output shold be JSON
Also the chatbot should ask for the user name, profession and add this context to the responses 
Use System prompt and ensure the chatbot as friendly AI assistant
(1) Ensure output is valid json format, focused and not too long
(2) Ensure the conversation is friendly, human language, not too forma
(3) Ask follow-up questions before long answers
(4) If the user starts with hi/hello, start with a warm greeting
(5) if the user is stuck, guide them and motivate them to ask the right question, do not guess
(6) Avoid unsafe output


